<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>MongoChat</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body class="home-body">
  <h1 class="home-title">Welcome to <span class="highlight">MongoChat</span> 💬</h1>
  <p class="home-subtitle">A lightweight chat app built with Node.js, Express, MongoDB & EJS.</p>

  <h3 class="home-section-title">What you can do here:</h3>
  <ul class="feature-list">
    <li>➕ Add a new chat</li>
    <li>✏️ Edit existing messages</li>
    <li>🗑️ Delete chats</li>
    <li>📂 View all chats in one place</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="button-group">
    <a href="/chats"><button class="btn">View All Chats</button></a>
    <a href="/chats/new"><button class="btn">Add New Chat</button></a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
